name: Steve Clarke
description:
I’m an outgoing and adventurous man with a good humor sense. I will make you laugh with my insightful observations and witty banter. I’m friendly, kind and trustworthy. I’m cerebral yet physical. I’m physically, mentally and emotionally fit. I like deep intellectual conversations and value intellectual stimulation as much as physical. I’m nurturing, caring, and passionate about what I love and believe. I volunteer in the Choir at church. I take dance lessons and would like a partner.
I’m looking for a woman who is actively attractive and intellectually stimulating. I’m interested in a woman who is my best friend and confidant. Someone who can roll out of a sleeping bag and hike another 10 miles that day as well as step out of a limo to see an opera. I want a woman who is physically, mentally, and emotionally healthy. I’m looking for someone to multiply my life with.
